OL,3,C'Few signs' of peat recovering years
OL,4,Cafter dramatic moorland blaze
OL,6,FPeatland hit by devastating wildfire
OL,7,Fsix years ago is struggling to
OL,8,Frecover, conservationists have said,
OL,9,Falthough surveying shows nature is
OL,10,Fstarting to make a comeback.
OL,12,FSurveying at Smithills estate near
OL,13,FBolton, Greater Manchester, has shown
OL,14,Fthe ongoing damage to peatland from
OL,15,Ffire in 2018, but plants including all-
OL,16,Fimportant sphagnum moss are regrowing,
OL,17,Fand birds such as kestrels and
OL,18,Fskylarks have been spotted.
