OL,3,C'Few signs' of peat recovering years
OL,4,Cafter dramatic moorland blaze
OL,6,FThe site, a mosaic of grassland,
OL,7,Ffarmland, moorland, woodland, wooded
OL,8,Fravines and bog habitats, was bought
OL,9,Fin two stages by the Woodland Trust in
OL,10,F2015 and 2017, with plans to restore
OL,11,Fand better manage the countryside,
OL,12,Fstreams and woodland for wildlife and
OL,13,Fthe local community.
OL,15,FBut in 2018 devastating wildfire
OL,16,Fduring the summer drought damaged
OL,17,Fabout a third of the estate, which
OL,18,Fincludes Winter Hill, harming moorland
OL,19,Fand wildlife and killing about 2,000
OL,20,Ftrees in the upland areas of the site.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
