OL,3,C'Few signs' of peat recovering years
OL,4,Cafter dramatic moorland blaze
OL,6,FEmergency services worked day and
OL,7,Fnight for 41 days to tackle the blaze.
OL,9,FSix years on, moorland surveys have
OL,10,Fbeen taking place, surveying two metre
OL,11,Fby two metre squares in selected sites
OL,12,Fto chart the wildlife and plants, and
OL,13,Fthe peat has also been measured.
OL,15,FSmithills site manager Oliver
OL,16,FStainthorpe, of the Woodland Trust,
OL,17,Fsaid: "During the fire all the peat
OL,18,Fmass was damaged in some way, but on
OL,19,Faverage 20cm of peat was completely
OL,20,Flost and burnt away.
OL,26,@yD@GOU
