OL,3,C'Few signs' of peat recovering years
OL,4,Cafter dramatic moorland blaze
OL,6,F"There are still very few signs of
OL,7,Fthis recovering. The grim reality is
OL,8,Fthat it is takes something like 200
OL,9,Fyears to regenerate the peat to how it
OL,10,Fwas.
OL,12,F"It shows the damage catastrophic
OL,13,Fevents, which are more likely due to
OL,14,Fclimate change, can have on nature."
OL,16,FBut he said: "It is not all doom and
OL,17,Fgloom, nature is bouncing back in some
OL,18,Fways.
