OL,3,C'Few signs' of peat recovering years
OL,4,Cafter dramatic moorland blaze
OL,6,FThe peatland on the site was not in
OL,7,Fgood condition before the blaze, as it
OL,8,Fhad been artificially drained for
OL,9,Fwater to be used in industry, the
OL,10,FWoodland Trust said.
OL,12,FWork such as putting in "leaky dams"
OL,13,Fto slow runoff were carried out to
OL,14,Frestore land immediately after the
OL,15,Ffire damage and the next stage will be
OL,16,Frestoring it as a whole.
