OL,3,C'Few signs' of peat recovering years
OL,4,Cafter dramatic moorland blaze
OL,6,FThe team have also been identifying
OL,7,Fthe location and characteristics of
OL,8,Fdrains in the moorland, to contribute
OL,9,Fto restoration plans to reduce water
OL,10,Fflow and rewet the moors.
OL,12,FMr Stainthorpe said: "Our key aim is
OL,13,Fthe restoration of the site, Smithills
OL,14,Fis blessed with a mosaic of
OL,15,Fhabitats,peatlands and uplands oak
OL,16,Fwoodland and upland wet woodland.
OL,18,F"Improved heathlands will increase
OL,19,Flocal biodiversity, capture carbon,
OL,20,Fand decrease flood risk."
