OL,3,C'Few signs' of peat recovering years
OL,4,Cafter dramatic moorland blaze
OL,6,FAnd he said: "As well as restoration,
OL,7,Fwe must try protecting the site from
OL,8,Fsuch a devastating incident occurring
OL,9,Fagain, this summer we have had
OL,10,Fvolunteers doing fire patrols to
OL,11,Fdetect any threats.
OL,13,F"Nature can bounce back but the damage
OL,14,Fcaused from such a catastrophic event
OL,15,Fcan take hundreds of years to
OL,16,Fovercome," he said.
